{{more footnotes|date=January 2014}} <!--- Don't mess with this line! ---><!--- Replace Subject of my article with the subject, and the ... after is with whatever your subject is. ---> <!--- Write your article below this line ---> '''''Processing Magazine''''' is a monthly trade magazine that covers [[process manufacturing]]. It serves manufacturers of food and kindred products, textiles, industrial [[chemicals]], plastic materials, synthetic resins, [[petroleum]], [[natural gas]] and [[pharmaceuticals]].<ref name="bpaww">{{cite web|url=http://www.bpaww.com/Bpaww_com/ProductManagement/PDFDisplay.aspx?statement_id=88822&pk=niajovrl3filrdxrsi3qnmt5|title=Product Management|work=Bpaww|accessdate=9 February 2014}}</ref> In June 2013, it had a circulation of 70,599 copies.<ref name="bpaww"/> It was established in 1987 by Putman Publishing Company and was acquired by Grand View Media Group in 2005. Grand View Media Group is a wholly owned subsidiary of [[EBSCO Industries|EBSCO Industries, Inc.]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ebscoind.com/GrandViewMediaGroup.asp|title=Grand View Media Group|work=EBSCO Industries, Inc.|accessdate=9 February 2014}}</ref> The magazine has its headquarters in [[Birmingham, Alabama]].<ref>{{cite web|title=Contact Us|url=http://www.processingmagazine.com/advertise/|work=Processing Magazine|accessdate=25 December 2015}}</ref>
